# Sūra VII.: A’rāf, or the Heights

### Section 8

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/007/007_059.gif)

59. Laqad arsaln<u>a</u> noo<u>h</u>an il<u>a</u> qawmihi faq<u>a</u>la
y<u>a</u> qawmi oAAbudoo All<u>a</u>ha m<u>a</u> lakum min il<u>a</u>hin
ghayruhu innee akh<u>a</u>fu AAalaykum AAa<u>tha</u>ba yawmin
AAa*<u>th</u>*eem**in**

59\. We sent Noah to his people.  
He said: "O my people!  
Worship God! ye have  
No other god but Him.  
I fear for you the Punishment  
Of a dreadful Day!

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/007/007_060.gif)

60. Q<u>a</u>la almalao min qawmihi inn<u>a</u> lanar<u>a</u>ka fee
<u>d</u>al<u>a</u>lin mubeen**in**

60\. The leaders of his people  
Said: "Ah! we see thee  
Evidently wandering (in mind)."

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/007/007_061.gif)

61. Q<u>a</u>la y<u>a</u> qawmi laysa bee <u>d</u>al<u>a</u>latun
wal<u>a</u>kinnee rasoolun min rabbi alAA<u>a</u>lameen**a**

61\. He said: "O my people!  
No wandering is there  
In my (mind): on the contrary  
I am an apostle from  
The Lord and Cherisher  
Of the Worlds!

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/007/007_062.gif)

62. Oballighukum ris<u>a</u>l<u>a</u>ti rabbee waan<u>s</u>a<u>h</u>u
lakum waaAAlamu mina All<u>a</u>hi m<u>a</u> l<u>a</u> taAAlamoon**a**

62\. "I but fulfil towards you  
The duties of my Lord's mission:  
Sincere is my advice to you,  
And I know from God  
Something that ye know not.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/007/007_063.gif)

63. Awa AAajibtum an j<u>a</u>akum <u>th</u>ikrun min rabbikum
AAal<u>a</u> rajulin minkum liyun<u>th</u>irakum walitattaqoo
walaAAallakum tur<u>h</u>amoon**a**

63\. "Do ye wonder that  
There hath come to you  
A message from your Lord,  
Through a man of your own  
People, to warn you,—  
So that ye may fear God  
And haply receive His Mercy?"

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/007/007_064.gif)

64. Faka<u>thth</u>aboohu faanjayn<u>a</u>hu wa**a**lla<u>th</u>eena
maAAahu fee alfulki waaghraqn<u>a</u> alla<u>th</u>eena
ka<u>thth</u>aboo bi-<u>a</u>y<u>a</u>tin<u>a</u> innahum k<u>a</u>noo
qawman AAameen**a**

64\. But they rejected him,  
And We delivered him,  
And those with him,  
In the Ark:  
But We overwhelmed  
In the Flood those  
Who rejected Our Signs.  
They were indeed  
A blind people!

